        <h2 id="pass-actions">PASS ACTIONS</h2>
        <p>Once per team turn. Steps:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Declare Target Square and Measure Range</li>
            <li>Test for Accuracy</li>
            <li>Optional: Passing Interference</li>
            <li>Optional: Catching the Ball</li>
